exact h2
```

This completes the proof. We've shown that `iIndepFun (fun p => rewardByCount A R p.1 (p.2 + 1)) (P.prod (Bandit.streamMeasure ν))` holds by proving that it's equivalent to `iIndepFun (fun (n : ℕ) => rewardByCount A R a n) (P.prod (Bandit.streamMeasure ν))`, which was already proven in `iIndepFun_rewardByCount'`.
